- It's OK.

532
00:32:37,706 --> 00:32:39,906
Lexie made a good call,
I've got it under control.

533
00:32:39,992 --> 00:32:44,578
- What do we got?
- Let me finish, Derek. I got this.

534
00:32:49,618 --> 00:32:51,551
