00:33:10,071 --> 00:33:12,422
Start-up costs alone,
never mind the FDA, Derek...

540
00:33:12,524 --> 00:33:17,543
Today, I watched Meredith perform
an emergency craniotomy by herself.

541
00:33:18,780 --> 00:33:22,865
She was perfect. She's
got her mother's talent.

542
00:33:22,967 --> 00:33:26,719
She's got her
mother's looks, Richard.

