00:33:27,722 --> 00:33:31,258
What if she has her
mother's disease?

544
00:33:31,359 --> 00:33:35,261
Ellis was young when it started.

545
00:33:35,363 --> 00:33:40,199
Every time Meredith forgets her keys
or asks what day of the week it is, I...

