that should go down with some time.

554
00:34:18,690 --> 00:34:20,123
I don't have boobs.

555
00:34:21,476 --> 00:34:23,777
- I don't have boobs?
- You don't have boobs.

556
00:34:25,664 --> 00:34:28,048
- Mom?
- She was scared.

557
00:34:28,150 --> 00:34:30,133
Now, she's just happy you're OK.

558
00:34:33,305 --> 00:34:37,323
- You're the man.
- No, you're the man.

559
00:34:42,113 --> 00:34:45,682
Roy Henley has end-stage
