that they're estranged.

581
00:36:00,959 --> 00:36:05,861
- That's not a reason.
- Dr. Yang?

582
00:36:05,963 --> 00:36:07,430
Do you have something to add?

583
00:36:08,499 --> 00:36:10,600
No.

584
00:36:10,702 --> 00:36:13,085
You don't believe that having
a support system in place

